snippet.title: Ball Turn | Wild Games Dev
snippet.description:
Android Link : https://play.google.com/store/apps/de...

Endless path following and bouncing between the walls. As far as you go the more difficult it will be.

Tap the screen at the right moment to change the ball's path and try not to fall. Collect cubes to unlock new collors for the ball.

How long can you go?
